reenwood|location=Santa Barbara, CA|year=2017|isbn=978-1-4408-3513-1|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Macan|first=Edward|title=Rocking the Classics: English Progressive Rock and the Counterculture|url=https://archive.org/details/rockingclassicse0000maca|url-access=registration|year=1997|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-509887-7}}\n* {{cite book|last=MacDonald|first=Ian|authorlink=Ian MacDonald|year=2002|chapter=The Psychedelic Experience|title=Mojo Special Limited Edition: 1000 Days That Shook the World (The Psychedelic Beatles \u2013 April 1, 1965 to December 26, 1967)|location=London|publisher=Emap|pp=30\u201336|ref=harv|title-link=Mojo (magazine)#Special editions}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=MacDonald|first=Ian|title=Revolution in the Head: The Beatles' Records and the Sixties|url=https://archive.org/details/revolutioninhead0003macd|url-access=registration|page=[https://archive.org/details/revolutioninhead0003macd/page/124 124]|year=2007|publisher=Chicago Review Press|isbn=978-1-55652-733-3}}\n* {{cite book|last=Marcus|first=Greil|authorlink=Greil Marcus|chapter=The Beatles|editor=DeCurtis, Anthony |editor2=Henke, James |editor3=George-Warren, Holly |editor4=Miller, Jim|title=The Rolling Stone Illustrated History of Rock & Roll: The Definitive History of the Most Important Artists and Their Music|url=https://books.google.com.au/books/about/The_Rolling_Stone_Illustrated_History_of.html?id=ubWAht7N7zsC&redir_esc=y| year=1992|origyear=1979|publisher=Straight Arrow|location=New York, NY|isbn=0-679-73728-6|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Martin|first=Bill|authorlink=Bill Martin (philosophy)|title=Avant Rock: Experimental Music from the Beatles to Bjork|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CCLyCgAAQBAJ|year=2015|publisher=Open Court Publishing Company|isbn=978-0-8126-9939-5}}\n* {{cite book|last=Marwick|first=Arthur|authorlink=Arthur Marwick|title=The Sixties: Cultural Revolution in Britain, France, Italy, and the United States|year=2012|origyear=1998|publisher=Bloomsbury Reader|location=London|isbn=978-1-4482-0573-8|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|ref=harv|last=Miles|first=Barry|authorlink=Barry Miles|title=Paul McCartney: Many Years from Now|url=https://archive.org/details/paulmccartneyman00mile|url-access=registration|page=[https://archive.org/details/paulmccartneyman00mile/page/280 280]|date=1998|publisher=Henry Holt and Company|location=New York, NY|isbn=978-0-8050-5249-7}}\n* {{cite book|last=Miles|first=Barry|title=The Beatles Diary Volume 1: The Beatles Years|year=2001|publisher=Omnibus Press|location=London|isbn=0-7119-8308-9|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last1=Miles|first1=Barry|last2=Morgan|first2=Johnny|title=The Greatest Album Covers of All Time|year=2005|publisher=Collins & Brown|location=London|isbn=1843403013|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Millard|first=Andr\u00e9|title=Beatlemania: Technology, Business, and Teen Culture in Cold War America|year=2012|publisher=Johns Hopkins University Press|location=Baltimore, MD|isbn=978-1-4214-0525-4|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Miller|first=Terry E.|chapter=Overview|editor-last=Koskoff|editor-first=Ellen |title=Garland Encyclopedia of World Music, Volume 3: The United States and Canada|year=2000|publisher=Garland Publishing|isbn=0-8240-4944-6|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Moore|first=Allan F.|year=1997|title=The Beatles: Sgt. Pepper's Lonely Hearts Club Band|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=Cambridge, UK|isbn=978-0-521-57484-6|url={{google books |plainurl=y |id=4y-oDmH2YzYC}}|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last=Moore|first=Allan F.|title=Song Means: Analysing and Interpreting Recorded Popular Song|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=S6DeCwAAQBAJ|year=2016|origyear=2012|publisher=Routledge|location=Abingdon, UK; New York, NY|isbn=978-1-4094-3802-1|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book|last2=Wardle|first2=Ben|last1=Morgan|first1=Johnny|title=The Art of the LP: Classic Album Covers 1955\u20131995|year=2015|origyear=2010|publisher=Sterling|location=New York,